== [    BASIC ] ============================================================================================
   MNEMONIC: bsf [ENC: DEFAULT, MAP: 0F, OPC: 0xBC]
     LENGTH:  3
        SSZ: 64
       EOSZ: 32
       EASZ: 64
   CATEGORY: BITBYTE
    ISA-SET: I386
    ISA-EXT: BASE
 EXCEPTIONS: NONE
 ATTRIBUTES: HAS_MODRM CPUFLAG_ACCESS 
  OPTIMIZED: 0F BC C1 

